The paper focuses on human-robot interaction, specifically on disambiguating verbal requests through visualisation. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) category. Additionally, the paper involves a robot, which suggests that it could also belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) category. The use of visualisation methods also suggests that the paper could belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also involves natural language processing, which suggests that it could belong to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) category. Finally, the paper involves objective and subjective measures, which suggests that it could also belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) category.
